to PluginCollection::findPath and it is returning NULL when the error occurs for the first time

This is in the wrong order:
```
        Configure::delete('plugins');
        $plugins = new PluginCollection();
        $path = $plugins->findPath('TestPlugin');
```

Should be:
```
        $plugins = new PluginCollection();
        Configure::delete('plugins');
        $path = $plugins->findPath('TestPlugin');
